{"tid":1382881,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［策略討論］獻策淋熄催淚彈","createTime":"2019-07-29T14:43:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T10:42:51.000Z","uid":266273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d2cc21d820525a8b1e1b6f4f184e7b0ffc12c2d2","tid":1382881,"uid":266273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:43:53.000Z","msg":"第一次開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望幫到少少呢場運動，關於淋熄蛋蛋<br />\n<br />\n早前聽過煙霧隊用雪糕筒淋熄蛋蛋，覺得好神奇，但未知實際執行係點，始終發夢唔喺最前線<br />\n岩先睇到呢條片，第一個問題諗：有無<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">更快方法</span></span></strong>！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjRm1k3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjRm1k3.png&h=dcfc1080&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hOjG1k4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhOjG1k4.png&h=68cc4aba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/29/223448_c17ab7c4746aa4a9c76cccd3bc76ac9e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F29%2F223448_c17ab7c4746aa4a9c76cccd3bc76ac9e.png&h=e577f51d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/29/223450_4d52f0596f5921d1d267f1a4d2a314cb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F29%2F223450_4d52f0596f5921d1d267f1a4d2a314cb.png&h=11ae5ef7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/29/223452_031058f72fd5c6cb07f1c2de51a4332d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F29%2F223452_031058f72fd5c6cb07f1c2de51a4332d.png&h=68029678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://touch.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2397446087181093&amp;id=1683158261943216&amp;preview_rid=2397460813846287\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftouch.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2397446087181093%26id%3D1683158261943216%26preview_rid%3D2397460813846287&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiYR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=8c18da57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://touch.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2397446087181093&amp;id=1683158261943216&amp;preview_rid=2397460813846287</a><br />\n<br />\n忽發奇想：倒轉個筒，封一封底，倒水落筒，一野cup落去係咪會再快D熄？<br />\n<br />\n此Po旨在拋磚引玉，希望巴絲都可以講下自己意見。如果呢個方法work，將<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大大提升效率</span></strong></span>。尤其依加D狗好中意一射射幾粒咁射，D過期蛋又嗆過之前，效率決定一切！"},{"pid":"d2f282780f83f1dab358d11b2358500873203c1a","tid":1382881,"uid":266273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:27:11.000Z","msg":"自推，希望幫到煙霧隊手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6375f6dcba14cefd487573427412a659522d9885","tid":1382881,"uid":23511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DjWiknt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDjWiknt.png&h=b25c59b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有無可能用到消防栓？ 可以既話 盡量將防線設係消防栓附近"},{"pid":"f2198e308bfb9d1c606281097747c203825609d3","tid":1382881,"uid":266273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6375f6dcba14cefd487573427412a659522d9885","tid":1382881,"uid":23511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DjWiknt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDjWiknt.png&h=b25c59b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有無可能用到消防栓？ 可以既話 盡量將防線設係消防栓附近"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:32:41.000Z","msg":"發夢喺上環站有見到，但無人用，都唔識用，係咪要有喉？"},{"pid":"1ab178929ada85be0a9375ca012bc173f35bf6b5","tid":1382881,"uid":100775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019